{"tid":970520,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"其實咁樣有冇機會？","createTime":"2019-01-06T01:37:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-06T01:53:50.000Z","uid":4816,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"01f20f7eeeb85b98d4c7b8b78e7653bcae5ea99a","tid":970520,"uid":4816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T01:37:42.000Z","msg":"同個女仔做左兩年同事，近幾個月開始熟絡，日日都會whatsapp 一齊食lunch。<br />\n<br />\n咁我約佢單獨行山打波食飯佢都會岀黎，同佢岀街佢會講好多佢屋企，教會野比我聽，我問佢感情狀況/往事都好樂意同我講，岀街大家都有講有笑咁。佢已經單身5年。<br />\n<br />\n我本身社交圈子細又唔鐘意social, 個女仔同我講佢都係唔鐘意social 既人黎。我地有時會互請對方食野，佢又有時又會買d 小禮物比我。 最近佢都有約我去做義工，其實我有冇機<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：米8 樣子ok，但個女仔大我可能有10年<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"813f0a4dc259d4a6f2474f2ba69829095002b1b1","tid":970520,"uid":146299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T01:38:59.000Z","msg":"教會野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed717f47f511fc61159e7d8913bb3cc1fda378bb","tid":970520,"uid":40478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T01:43:09.000Z","msg":"佢急住搵人埋單姐"},{"pid":"98899f8e5b8a7ed780589ca1cdcfb63c6722d9fd","tid":970520,"uid":171534,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T01:45:13.000Z","msg":"人哋幾歲都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a43687501198a57991af6cb4ec4c4fecfa3a2122","tid":970520,"uid":1060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T01:50:40.000Z","msg":"有"},{"pid":"e98fe64c7e1ded463de20087af503d4a0900e980","tid":970520,"uid":4816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98899f8e5b8a7ed780589ca1cdcfb63c6722d9fd","tid":970520,"uid":171534,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T01:45:13.000Z","msg":"人哋幾歲都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T01:53:39.000Z","msg":"我知佢大概幾歲就夠啦<img s